title: Aiglon du Lamentin FC
text:
L'Aiglon du Lamentin Football Club is a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club of <a href="Martinique">Martinique</a>, playing in the town of <a href="Le%20Lamentin">Lamentin</a>.
They play in the Martinique's first division, the <a href="Martinique%20Championnat%20National">Martinique Championnat National</a>
